會揀D貴呱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:50:25.000Z","msg":"外國豬肉, 價錢同品質都比支那豬好<br />\n<br />\n起碼無元素表RISK<br />\n<br />\n梅林豬早兩日先發現殘餘獸藥<br />\n<br />\n無人會想去食獸藥掛..."},{"pid":"34a02004e65a6b417ea44b644d33196694d41e0f","tid":732494,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:51:48.000Z","msg":"食肉糜"},{"pid":"499810912077d865e7c01fb44003e0caa515a0b0","tid":732494,"uid":120499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:56:44.000Z","msg":"餐廳全部用凍豬肉<br />\n係屋企先用新鮮肉<br />\n香港政府之前將本地豬農收哂牌，淨係呢個量已經夠供每日一半以上。<br />\n<br />\n香港本地豬農同豆類製造商輸入大豆根本唔需要稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df565aba66b2bb427483c647f8d3c9b278aeb02","tid":732494,"uid":57329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:56:47.000Z","msg":"原來以前食嘅豆腐係美國原料咁高級 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1e863f90943dacde6a057321a6ec81c1d82eff","tid":732494,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5df565aba66b2bb427483c647f8d3c9b278aeb02","tid":732494,"uid":57329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:56:47.000Z","msg":"原來以前食嘅豆腐係美國原料咁高級 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:59:05.000Z","msg":"好多人食野, 係唔知自己食緊邊度野<br />\n<br />\n一味以為食野就必定係支那<br />\n<br />\n所以以前, 好多人會驚「斷水斷糧」乜乜物物<br />\n<br />\n係近年班港豬被屌得多, 百屌成材, 先開始FACT FIND, 發現支那食物根本不太重要"},{"pid":"23a3104e431aa7265c5e7e15f921b662302f9105","tid":732494,"uid":60408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"819d15b4503a78b4217165135b65dadddd903656","tid":732494,"uid":179938,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:38:46.000Z","msg":"食丹麥豬囉，on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T04:01:19.000Z","msg":"岩, 明明歐州入口既豬安全好多, 支那豬都唔知放左咩化學元素去養"},{"pid":"da2a3f0696